[genericglass OldFashioned] Serving Glass: Old Fashioned W/ice

In Mixing Glass With Ice Add:
1 1/2 oz [genericingredient Brandy] Don Pedro Brandy
2 tsp [genericingredient Lemon Juice] Lemon Juice
2 tsp [genericingredient Orange Juice] Orange Juice
1 1/2 tsp Simple Syrup
1 tsp [genericingredient Maraschino Cherry Juice] Maraschino Cherry Juice
Shake and Strain

